-- Turkey's Isbank sells 273 mln lira NPL portfolio for 44 mln lira
-- 
-- Wed Jun 04, 2014 10:47AM EDT
-- None



ISTANBUL, June 4 (Reuters) - Turkish lender Isbank <ISCTR.IS> said on Wednesday it sold its non-performing loans portfolio worth 273 million lira ($129 million) to Girisim asset management for 44 million lira.

The bank made the statement to Istanbul Stock Exchange.